{"tid":180311,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"秀智短髮似新垣結衣？　網民唔受落：冇晒仙氣","createTime":"2017-03-31T00:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-01T10:20:32.000Z","uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88a0560d820dee7f3d48d4007270b3aff951b90c","tid":180311,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T00:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2425/d2425391.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2425%2Fd2425391.jpg&h=51c8c040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0SCOoTql.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0SCOoTql.jpg&h=2ec965f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n韓國「國民初戀」秀智近日忙於孖男星李鍾碩合作拍攝新劇《當你熟睡時》，出道7年來都係以長髮形象示人嘅秀智，今次就為劇集剪短髮。<br />\n<br />\n雖然早前已有粉絲影到秀智拍攝時嘅造型，但都係側面照居多，而且拍攝時秀智經常紮起頭髮。於最近公開嘅影片中，秀智就穿上白色衫現身，向大家正式展示新造型，不過粉絲就似乎唔多受落呢個髮型，留言「好男仔頭」、「剪壞了」、「冇晒仙氣」、「感覺想走新垣結衣風，但扮唔到」、「駕馭唔到短髮」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，秀智跟JYP事務所嘅合約將於明日到期，不過截至目前為止，JYP方面都表示雙方仍未續約，仲商討緊某啲細節，不過秀智拍攝新劇時，所有行程都有JYP嘅經理人陪伴。"},{"pid":"95307113978d981cc38a014e0f2a5ee803d12833","tid":180311,"uid":85243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T00:49:54.000Z","msg":"就算長髮都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21c57066c72271caf0d358b21e032b509dd6b6ff","tid":180311,"uid":70361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:03:56.000Z","msg":"變撚左8~90年代咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌左出聲"},{"pid":"6cb1102fd9abcca4906ffefbef160ce59da33e1b","tid":180311,"uid":2022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:13:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b5fe03b26507539a8eb3f7f228e71036f87cc84","tid":180311,"uid":16087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-31T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"內田真禮"},{"pid":"472a390eff001679983c2e189c6ba4f3f9c77143","tid":180311,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c